OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with strong sunshine.
OL,6,FAfter a warm start, temperatures will
OL,7,Fquickly rise to bring a very hot day
OL,8,Facross the region with light winds and
OL,9,Fhigh humidity into the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry and very warm
OL,12,Fthrough the evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunshine. A very warm and muggy night
OL,14,Fto come.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry, warm and sunny start.
OL,17,FTurning even hotter on Thursday with
OL,18,Fextreme heat continuing and high
OL,19,Fhumidity. Perhaps a little cloudier at
OL,20,Ftimes in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
